data.description: The Landing collection provides single level, flats-style condos, in elevator-serviced buildings with bike storage, private garages, secure entry access, modern architecture and wonderful views from the Rooftop Deck!  This beautiful Plan-2 home offers an open concept main living area, anchored by a spacious Chefs kitchen. This home boasts crisp “White Icing” cabinetry, quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances and upgraded flooring throughout. It offers an owner’s suite with a bathroom and a walk-in closet, and a secondary bedroom and full bathroom. This light-filled corner unit features a spacious gathering room, and a café with adjoining deck overlooking the waterfront park. This new home community will boast a variety of amenities for residents, including a public park, with picnic areas, a playground, a dock, walking path along the estuary and more!
